title: Hard Disk Manager 15 Backup & Recovery Compact 10.1.25.813
description:
Paragon Hard Disk Manager 15 Backup & Recovery Compact 10.1.25.813 (x86/x64) - CORE

Features

Easy backup & flexible restoration
Back up the operating system or even your entire hard disk - restore an entire disk, separate partitions or specific files

Backup Scheduler
Set it up once and backups will be managed automatically

Extra feature: partitioning tools
Create, format, delete partitions, assign / remove drive letter, set partition active / inactive

Embedded Recovery Media Builder 3.0
Create a bootable rescue media to boot the system in case of emergency.

Homepage http://www.paragon-software.com/home/brh/
